profile: Mac-Klean Northumberland is an Eco-Friendly interior/exterior Window and Vinyl cleaning specialist.  We use a Pure Water filtration system and an extendable water-fed pole which can reach heights of over 50 feet with ease.  Mac-Klean has dedicated professionals that will leave your property with beautiful spot-free shining windows, rejuvenated vinyl siding or both!  We service both residential and commercial buildings. Mac-Klean is fully insured and bondable.  Call us today!
